## Edunline font

`art/fonts/edunline*`

Edunline is a Freeware font by Brian Kent.

  The font(s) in this zip file were created by me (Brian Kent). All of my
  Fonts are Freeware, you can use them any way you want to (Personal use,
  Commercial use, or whatever).

  If you have a Font related site and would like to offer my fonts on your
